mdRecord.dcterms:title: 50th reunion Celebration of Floyd High School
mdRecord.dcterms:description: A booklet for the 50th reunion Celebration on June 20th, 1992 of Floyd High School classmates of 1939 - 1942. The booklet includes the schedule of events, photographs, stories, and statistics covering the school years 1939 through 1942.
mdRecord.dcterms:subject: School reunions
mdRecord.dcterms:provenance: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University. University Libraries
